data.description: Outstanding Home in the Heart of Saddle Brook on a Huge 80x130 Corner Lot! Cape Cod Style Home added a Massive Expansion just 8 Years Ago. Now has over 3500 Sq. Ft. of Living Space! First Floor Features Living Room, 2 Bedrooms, Eat-In Kitchen & Bath. Hardwood Flooring throughout is New & Refinished! Second Floor dazzles with Super Open Floor Plan of Living Room, Dining Room & Kitchen with gleaming Hardwood Flooring. Possible In Law Suite, Large Master Bedroom w/Walk-In Closet, Generous 2nd Bedroom, Modern Full Bath Tiled, Laundry Room & 3rd Bedroom finish the 2nd Floor. Partially finished Basement, 2nd Laundry Rm & Storage. All of this with an Incredible additional 2000 Sq Ft. 3 Car Finished Garage with Heat, AC & 10 Ft High Ceilings!! Fenced In Yard. Wide Driveway! 2 Zone Central Air/Heat, 200 & 100 Amp Services, Security Cameras, Shed & More! Close to All Major Highways & Transportation! Truly a Must See! In-Law Suite! Don't Miss This Home! Very Very Rare Opportunity!!
